headline: Franklin Templeton Announces Plan to Liquidate Putnam BioRevolution™ ETF
summary: SAN MATEO, Calif., September 19, 2025--Franklin Templeton today announced it will liquidate and dissolve Putnam BioRevolution™ ETF (SYNB). The liquidation is anticipated to occur on or about November 21, 2025, although the Fund may make dispositions of portfolio holdings prior to the liquidation date.
